  (864,'Sports','/Files/News/News451493812343720.jpg','Sol Campbell not invited by Tottenham to final game at White Hart Lane','Sol Campbell has been snubbed by Tottenham in plans to mark the final match at White Hart Lane later this month. Campbell became a hate figure among fans following his decision to quit Spurs and join their deadly north London rivals Arsenal in 2001. And with the countdown firmly on to the last ever game at the Lane, club officials have decided not to risk the event being upstaged by Campbell''s appearance on the pitch at full-time.','2017-05-03','9:30:00','http://talksport.com/football/sol-campbell-not-invited-tottenham-final-game-white-hart-lane-170503237707','talkSPORT','Active'),
