  (870,'Sports','/Files/News/News511493812349338.jpg','''Fixed, done and stronger'' - Manchester United striker Zlatan Ibrahimovic in positive mood after knee surgery','Zlatan Ibrahimovic says he feels \"stronger\" following surgery in the United States of America to repair cruciate ligament damage to his knee. The 35-year-old Manchester United striker forward hobbled out of United''s Europa League quarter-final win over Anderlecht on April 20, with his future uncertain as he faced a lengthy spell of rehabilitation.','2017-05-02','5:45:00','http://talksport.com/football/fixed-done-and-stronger-manchester-united-striker-zlatan-ibrahimovic-positive-mood-after','talkSPORT','Active'),
