  (2505,'/Files/News/News731499238727239.jpg','Rajnikanth’s daughter Soundarya is officially divorced - Shocking divorces in Bollywood  | The Times of India','Rajinikanth''s daughter Soundarya has finally parted ways with husband Ashwin. Their marriage came to an end on Tuesday when the principal family court judge Maria Clatta formalised the separation. The two were married for seven years and have a four-year-old son. Reports say that the court proceedings went on for seven months but were smooth and the decision of getting a divorce was mutual. The couple was firm on ending their marriage but neither the terms of settlement nor the custody of their son have been revealed till now. The couple, married on September 3, 2010. Lawyers privy to the divorce proceedings said the couple had been living separately for about seven months now, and their misunderstanding over various issues reached a point of no return earlier than that.\n  \n  \n  Though initially the news of marital discord was being denied by both Soundarya and Ashwin, the fact that Soundarya kept saying that she always felt proud to identify herself as ''Soundarya Rajinikanth'', triggered debate over the status of their marriage.\n  \n  They later came out in the open about the ongoing case and appeared in court together. The separate proceedings were smooth and without much ado.',NULL,NULL,'http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/shocking-divorces-in-bollywood/rajnikanths-daughter-soundarya-is-officially-divorced/photostory/59451564.cms',NULL,'Active'),
